    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition, offering a reliable driving experience for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small door dings, and the interior shows signs of regular use, including some wear on the driver's seat upholstery. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will eventually need some routine suspension work and the tires have about 40% tread remaining. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that starts every time and is ready for daily commuting.",
